data.description: WOW WOW WOW....This charming property offers a perfect combination of comfort and style. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a two-car garage, this home is a dream come true. Its proximity to schools makes it the ideal choice for families, but what makes it even more special is its incredible outdoor space.    With an adorable fully fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxing moments, this property also has a 220V electrical hookup. Ideal for hooking up your RV or other equipment that requires this type of power! Plus, its versatile additional garage space in the backyard, measuring 24 x 40 x 15, offers endless possibilities.    Don't miss the opportunity to explore this home full of comforts and security. Property is completely fenced! Contact us today to schedule a visit and discover how this property can fulfill your dreams.  Close to I75, SR 200, CR 484, hospitals, schools, colleges, resturants, hotels, shopping and entertainment.
